Russians Again Pushing Disinformation in U.S., Facebook and Twitter SayThe group that interfered in the 2016 election is using fake accounts and a website set up to look like a left-wing news site, the companies said.The revelation is the first public evidence that the group is trying to repeat its efforts from four years ago to help President Trump.

Trump Spread Multiple Conspiracy Theories. Here Are Their Roots.In an interview with Fox News on Monday, President Trump spread these unfounded ideas about recent protests that have been circulating online for months.
